                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-dark"><span class="inline">About Me</span></h2>
                    <p class="text-lg font-light mb-4">My name is Zouheir Mohamed, a passionate PHP backend developer. I specialize in crafting robust and scalable web applications using modern PHP frameworks such as Laravel and Symfony.</p>
                    <p class="text-white leading-relaxed">With a keen interest in web development, I have hands-on experience in building and optimizing backend systems to deliver seamless and efficient user experiences. My expertise extends to database design, API development, and server-side logic implementation.</p>
                    <p class="text-white leading-relaxed">I thrive in collaborative environments, where I can contribute my skills to create innovative solutions and solve complex challenges. Continuously staying updated with the latest industry trends, I am committed to delivering high-quality code that meets the highest standards of performance and security.</p>
                    <p class="text-white leading-relaxed">Outside of coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open-source projects, and enjoying a good cup of coffee. Let's connect and discuss how I can bring value to your next project.</p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4">
                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mohamedzouheir/" target="_blank">{{ component('button', {text: 'Linkedin' , icon : 'fa-brands fa-linkedin'}) }}</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
